customLabels.label: I-co-stimulator engabonakali (ICOS) iyiphrotheni etholakala phezu kwamaseli amhlophe egazi nakwamanye amaseli omdlavuza. Amaseli amhlophe egazi ayingxenye yamasosha omzimba (isistimu yemvelo yomzimba yokuzivikela). Amaphrotheni e-ICOS adlala indima ebalulekile ekulawuleni amasosha omzimba. Lokhu kuhlola kukala umthamo we-ICOS egazini lakho. Ezinye izinhlobo zokwelashwa zingase zikufanele kakhudlwana uma unamazinga aphezulu e-ICOS akhona egazini lakho. Lokhu kuhlola kungasiza odokotela babikezele ukuthi yikuphi ukwelashwa komdlavuza okungasebenzela kahle wena.
